        <div class="mw-50">
            <h3 class="">WordPress Is Easy To Use Especially For Beginners</h3>
            <p>
                One of the main reasons WordPress is so the go to website solution for the internet community is because of its easy to use user interface. The WordPress dashboard is very simple in it's design and the learning curve for getting basic tasks accomplished like adding pages and search engine optimization are very low. On top that features like WordPress Plugins & WordPress Themes make it a doable for anyone without a little bit of patience to spin up a WordPress website in minutes.   
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mw-50">
            <h3 class="">WordPress Plugins Make Adding Features To Your Website Easy</h3>
            <p>
                <i>What is a WordPress plugin?</i>  WordPress Plugins are additional features that can add simple and complex functionality to your website. These extra features you can add with a few simple clicks can help you do things like. Implement a contact form system that notifys you through email, add a login system that gives users a customized expiernece when using your web app, add and manage an entire online store from the dashboard of your wordpress website.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mw-50">
            <h3 class="">WordPress Themes Make It Easy To Design </h3>
            <p>
                <i>What are WordPress Themes?</i> WordPress Themes very much like WordPress Plugins are additional pieces of code you can add to your website to improve it's appearance. WordPress Themes can give you professional Grade look to your website and save you a few hundred dollars in design work.
            </p>
        </div>

        
